description:
&lt;p&gt;We are excited to be able to offer the opportunity for a senior clinical psychologist to join the Sheffield CAMHS team. This is a large and dynamic team with lots of opportunities for CPD and close work with other psychologists, as well as other professionals within the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The teams consist of therapists, psychologists, psychiatrists, mental health nurses and mental health practitioners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone with skills and knowledge of neurodevelopmental assessments, as well as attachment experience and other therapy experience (eg: CBT, EMDR, CAT, etc) . There will be an opportunity to work in a number of pathways.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please come and visit and see what we do !&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;30 hours per week.&lt;/p&gt;
